## âœ¨ Features  
- â• Create new blog posts  
- âœï¸ Update existing posts  
- âŒ Delete posts  
- â¤ï¸ Like posts (with persistence)  
- ğŸ“¦ JSON storage with autoâ€‘increment IDs  
- ğŸ”Œ Fileâ€‘path injection for flexible persistence  

